text: Sabah IV Ahmad Al-Jaber Al-Sabah GCB (Hon) (; 16 June 1929 â€“ 29 September 2020)Profile of Sabah IV Ahmad Al-Jaber Al-Sabah was the 5th Emir of Kuwait and the Commander of the Military of Kuwait. He was sworn in on 29 January 2006 after confirmation by the National Assembly of Kuwait. In July 2020, Al- Sabah was hospitalized at the Mayo Clinic in Rochester, Minnesota and had surgery. He died on 29 September 2020, aged 91. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1929 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from surgical complications Category:Emirs of Kuwait Category:Prime Ministers of Kuwait
